snippet.textDisplay: I clap my hands for KENTRELL. I still feel he is underrated,but it is what is. This young man or his management team has to be very smart with their planning. They are keeping most of the money in house , it appears. Just about every video I have seen from him has been low budget, i.e., in a house, park, car, gas station. Pretty much a video that can be filmed by any college student in 🎥 film/ arts who has a great eye. When I say this, it is far from a diss to YB & management. It is like more of a compliment.You give the people imagery without spending a fortune for a video. I am stating this only on the margin of comparison to other peoples favorite rappers like Drake, Jay Z, Nicki. This young man is so dope with the amount of music he puts out. The only thing I do wish to see him do is more collaborations with higher classed artist. I think it will truly diversify him and so call "A" list him. But, what ever we see you YB. GO OFF!💖💥💥💥💥
